    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like finish without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-new condition, with every surface, switch, and upholstery stitch appearing untouched. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. It comes with a complete service history, confirming its life of pampered care.",
