    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained vehicle that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? This car is in good shape and offers a smooth, dependable ride that you can count on! It has been consistently cared for, making it a fantastic choice for anyone seeking a high-quality, pre-owned vehicle that performs beautifully on the road.",
