    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this diamond in the rough! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic and affordable opportunity for a restoration enthusiast or someone looking for a dedicated parts vehicle. This is your chance to bring a classic back to life at a great entry-level price!",
